{"tid":1262621,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"嚇到屎都標","createTime":"2019-06-27T18:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T18:44:16.000Z","uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2dd348a4413ef50bf4a5a31a284a635833ca2be","tid":1262621,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:39:02.000Z","msg":"突然間聽到聲巨響 以為係無力或者益力多後果<br />\n原來係跣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />膠刀肺豉髀<br />\n好鬼擔心真係\\<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 但諗諗吓都係遲早嘅事...<br />\n然之後又覺得如果我都搵埋一份就無人真係關心佢<br />\n但又確實唔想留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又有少少好心酸咁睇到。。"},{"pid":"169b2b86fa0deaf4b5388610b19fbb94733f1f4b","tid":1262621,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:40:04.000Z","msg":"係見過最言行一致嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個超好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個人都好但就有啲係假好但佢真好<br />\n唔應該要咁 唔應該會咁囉覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼都識叫先啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4da81b2527a9cf2e94d95c1c736c69df4235c0","tid":1262621,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"仲要完全幫唔到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人實會揀前者但我即刻想掉咗手入面嗰個衝過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f11de8cfef93e7391c790d4da8593f86ca01d18","tid":1262621,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:44:16.000Z","msg":"有一半係唔想面對就逃避掂行掂過<br />\n另外嗰半係唔想後悔就逼住去面對久唔久望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋個親生仔都無我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}